snippet.title: PotC: New Horizons - Small fight.
snippet.description:
Raw un-altered footage showing CannonFX 3.0 in action in New Horizons Build 14 Beta 3.
Superior British naval force destroying its foe with overwhelming firepower.

Recorded with Nvidia ShadowPlay on a GTX 660ti.
